snippet.title: European War 5 intro
snippet.description:
From the Classical Age to the Industrial Age, spanning 2,000 years and 150 major battles
Conquer the world across 6 ages
8 great civilizations, 90 unique units, over 100 famous generals
Empire mode allows you to build a great dynasty
Recruit the famous generals of history
Discovery legendary weapons
Chase princesses of different states
The long-awaited diplomacy system
Please visit the official website http://www.ieasytech.com
